title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Leber, Jeradi, Burnsy, Krawczynski, Hasan
description: Eric Nordquist is in the big chair today, he is joined right away by Ben Leber. Talking the Kentucky Derby with Dick Jeradi. Gopher Illustrated's Ryan Burns commiserates with Nordo about the day that would've been the Gopher's first game of the season. Jon Krawczynsk scratches that NBA Bubble itch for us all. And The Athletic's Arif Hasan on everything Vikings.
